These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, snooker
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bongani
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, project-manager
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Game      | snooker     | backgammon |
| Cigar   | bongani | baccarat      |
| Job         | project-manager    | doctor      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, red
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, trike
1. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Color         | red      | fuchsia |
| Flower   | marigold | daisy    |
| Transport           | trike         | bike         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, british
There 2 different types of food: garlic, blueberry
1. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | zombie |
| Nationality         | british       | colombian       |
| Food   | blueberry       | garlic         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
House: modern, tower
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea
City: rome, berlin
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsazalea is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| House    | tower    | modern     |
| Flower       | poppy    | azalea |
| City   | rome | berlin    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
