The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, august
2 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| House       | modern | futuristic |
| Birthday         | january      | august  |
| Game   | bridge | mah-jongg   |

