.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, davidoff
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, zucchini
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Flower   | rose | zinnia   |
| Cigar   | davidoff          | cain   |
| Food         | artichoke     | zucchini |

 